{"tid":2146324,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐-籽樂","createTime":"2020-08-08T13:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T16:06:33.000Z","uid":66236,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2037ea35fcd782b2cde5c1a18e62cd82512daad5","tid":2146324,"uid":66236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCPYOVT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCPYOVT.png&h=0bd1c413&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWh0hPj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWh0hPj.png&h=a526a998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n$128一個餐，有主菜、野飲、餐湯加兩塊蒜蓉包<br />\n好好味嘅黃店外賣！<br />\n蕃茄湯夠濃，無味精<br />\n<br />\n飛魚籽煙三文魚白酒忌廉汁意粉，通常三文魚意粉，都係意粉還意粉，三文魚就捲成朵花擺係上面，但係佢足料到不得了！真係啖啖有三文魚同埋魚籽！<br />\n忌廉汁又唔會太膩，食完唔會頸渴個種！<br />\n<br />\n然後到肉眼- 外賣叫肉眼 其實真係有啲搏，但係佢係無令我失望，口感好好，juicy, 唔會煮到老哂<br />\n<br />\n嗚真係好抵- 仲要外賣完個樣都咁靚<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n題外話 - 佢係社企，請聽障同埋學校障礙嘅staff , 尼段時間都無放棄員工，食物又咁有質素，真係好值得我地支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd7af8d29acf38dbd38292a7026da4cf069d9b2","tid":2146324,"uid":56063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d1c6e46d857f9a810e887899f755019eac20fab","tid":2146324,"uid":127044,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:54:29.000Z","msg":"狗飯"},{"pid":"ac4ee947aa21c6a1e5fcb302d5e6ce68bf32b658","tid":2146324,"uid":281492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:56:04.000Z","msg":"個樣望落都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385d078a05cfdee65a93edeeb869ca8310cd934c","tid":2146324,"uid":13118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T15:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a96d408c726e6b88a71be5d3ae3391139942208","tid":2146324,"uid":